you. Are you among those who are beginning to conclude that, when all the
dust settles, the <PLACE country="US" form="NAM" gazref="IGDB:840" id="Pl-12" type="COUNTRY">U.S.</PLACE> may not find weapons of mass destruction in <PLACE country="IQ" form="NAM" gazref="IGDB:16897518" id="Pl-3" latLong="33.000°N 44.000°E" type="COUNTRY">Iraq</PLACE>?


 SEN. RICHARD LUGAR (R), <PLACE country="US" form="NAM" gazref="IGDB:449508" id="Pl-16" latLong="40.000°N 86.250°W" state="US-IN" type="CIVIL">INDIANA</PLACE> 
