that weapons of mass destruction are there, and likewise, that we will be
led to them by people knowledgeable in the <PLACE country="IQ" form="NOM" gazref="IGDB:16897518" id="Pl-17" latLong="33.000°N 44.000°E" type="COUNTRY">country</PLACE> as to where they are.
